title: BOARDWALK / TRANT HEIDELSTAM barks
description: Things Trant says to Mikael near the feld building.

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Don't worry, Mikael, you'll learn..."
dialogueTree.english: "Don't worry, Mikael, you'll learn all about it."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie martw się, Mikaelu, wszystkiego się dowiesz”.

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Fifty years ago this place was the..."
dialogueTree.english: "Fifty years ago this place was the heart of innovation."
dialogueTree.polish: „Pięćdziesiąt lat temu tu było centrum innowacji”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Пяцьдзесят гадоў таму тут быў цэнтр інавацый».

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Feld versus Tricentennial -- I wis..."
dialogueTree.english: "Feld versus Tricentennial -- I wish we could've witnessed that, Mikael."
dialogueTree.polish: „Feld kontra Tricentennial – szkoda, że nie mogliśmy tego oglądać, Mikaelu”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Фельд супраць Трыцэнтэнэрыя – шкада, што мы не маглі гэтага паглядзець, Мікаэль».

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""On the outside – ruins. But what a..."
dialogueTree.english: "On the outside – ruins. But what are ruins, Mikael? Detritus of lost epochs."
dialogueTree.polish: „Na zewnątrz – ruiny. Ale czym są ruiny, Mikaelu? Detrytem minionych epok”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Звонку — руіны. Але што такое руіны, Міхаэль? Дэтрытам мінулых эпох».

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""We are living in *very* interestin..."
dialogueTree.english: "We are living in *very* interesting times, Mikael."

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""Remind me to give you that collect..."
dialogueTree.english: "Remind me to give you that collection of essays on modern architecture, Mikael."
dialogueTree.polish: „Przypomnij mi, Mikaelu, żebym dał ci ten zbiór esejów przybliżających współczesną architekturę”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Нагадай мне, Мікаэль, каб я даў табе гэты збор эсэ, якія знаёмяць з сучаснай архітэктурай».

dialogueTree.title: Trant Heidelstam: ""The significance of all *this* is..."
dialogueTree.english: "The significance of all *this* is hard to overestimate."
